@node "Last Word" "Last Word"
@next "Main"
@prev "Descriptions"
@{fg highlight}                                 
                                 LAST WORD@{fg text}

   There are loads of things that I don't understand about Arexx, and about
   Rexxedit. The COPYEVENT and PEEKEVENT I can't fathom at all; if you can
   illuminate I would appreciate it. If anyone can direct me to text
   (other than the sparse words that came with Music-x) dealing with Arexx
   or Rexxedit, I would love to hear from you. 

   
   If you enjoy these macros, or have any comment to make, please drop a
   line to

